Package org.hibernate.query.criteria

Interface JpaCriteriaSelect<T>

All Superinterfaces:
CriteriaSelect<T>
All Known Subinterfaces:
JpaCriteriaQuery<T>, JpaSubQuery<T>
All Known Implementing Classes:
CriteriaDefinition, SqmSelectStatement, SqmSubQuery
public interface JpaCriteriaSelect<T> extends CriteriaSelect<T>
Extension of the JPA CriteriaSelect.
API Note:
This is different from JpaSelectCriteria. JPA added CriteriaSelect in version 3.2 while JpaSelectCriteria has existed for many releases prior. JPA's CriteriaSelect is intended for supporting its newly added set operations (union, interest, except).
